    "Additionally, some potential AI research avenues for the Metaverse are discussed.",
    "As the Metaverse becomes more prevalent and VR experiences become more advanced, the integration of AI with technologies such as IoT, blockchain, VR, AR, MR, and XR will continue to play an increasingly important role in shaping its development.",
